               </msIdentifier>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Varia: Image 1r: unidentified text, written in pencil. Illuminations added recently over text. Image 51r: The midpoint is marked with a small  text in a box of alternating red and black dots: መንፈቁ ለዳዊት. The Psalms are missing Pss 146-151. Several of the Canticles are missing. The base hand of the Song of Songs is the common version, but many additional lines from the scholars' edition are added interlinearly. The Praises of Mary begin with Monday and culminate in Sunday. Gate of Light is incomplete at the end due to illuminations painted over text.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <textLang/>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
